issue(id="0000" status="open")
  title Replace with a short issue title
  user-story
    as-a Replace with the primary user or operator role.
    i-want Replace with the capability or behavior they need.
    so-that Replace with the outcome or reason this matters.
  premise.
    Replace with the framing assumptions for the work, including the intended
    model, relevant current behavior, and any known risks or constraints.
  acceptance-criteria
    criterion Replace with a concrete, testable success condition.
    criterion Replace with another concrete, testable success condition.
  review-items
    item(status="covered") Replace with a review check that has been completed.
    item(status="open") Replace with a review concern or follow-up still to resolve.

